---
---

<section class="manifesto" id="manifesto" aria-labelledby="manifesto-heading">
  <div class="manifesto__container">

    <div class="manifesto__header">
      <h2 class="manifesto__title">What I'm Looking For</h2>
      <p class="manifesto__subtitle">My next chapter</p>
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto__layout">

      <!-- Left: bold statement -->
      <div class="manifesto__left">
        <div class="manifesto__avatar">
          <img src="/Me.jpg" alt="Alessandro Giordano" class="manifesto__avatar-img" />
        </div>
        <p class="manifesto__statement" id="manifesto-heading">
          I am looking for a <strong>leadership environment</strong> where design is treated as a <strong>strategic partner</strong> to business and engineering. My goal is to lead the vision for <strong>digital products</strong> that bridge the gap between human needs and technology, ultimately elevating the organization's overall <strong>design maturity.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: three pillars -->
      <div class="manifesto__right">

        <div class="manifesto__pillar">
          <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
          <div class="manifesto__pillar-content">
            <h3 class="manifesto__pillar-title">Create</h3>
            <p class="manifesto__pillar-body">I want to move beyond visuals to build the architectural backbone of digital products. I am searching for a space where I can turn deep insights into human-centered experiences that are functional, emotional, and inclusive, ensuring every design output drives a tangible user outcome.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__pillar">
          <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
          <div class="manifesto__pillar-content">
            <h3 class="manifesto__pillar-title">Collaborate</h3>
            <p class="manifesto__pillar-body">I thrive when leading cross-functional teams and aligning designers, engineers, and product managers around shared, high-impact goals. I value a leadership style rooted in transparency and empathy, where I can mentor individuals to leverage their strengths and overcome challenges to grow as professionals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__pillar">
          <span class="manifesto__num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
          <div class="manifesto__pillar-content">
            <h3 class="manifesto__pillar-title">Grow</h3>
            <p class="manifesto__pillar-body">I am seeking a role where I can shape design culture and operations at scale. I want to evolve experimental ideas into validated organizational practices, fostering a continuous cycle of knowledge that allows a product team to move faster without sacrificing quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tao-surface-brand-2-subtlest) 64%, var(--tao-surface-neutral-white));
    padding: var(--tao-spacing-xxxl) 0;
  }

  .manifesto__container {
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--tao-spacing-xl);
  }

  .manifesto__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--tao-spacing-xxxl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .manifesto__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--tao-spacing-xl);
  }

  .manifesto__title {
    font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--tao-text-default);
    margin: 0 0 var(--tao-spacing-xs);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .manifesto__subtitle {
    font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-md);
    color: var(--tao-text-subtle);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Avatar ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .manifesto__avatar {
    width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    border-radius: var(--tao-radius-circular);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: var(--tao-border-width-md) solid var(--tao-border-brand-1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px color-mix(in srgb, var(--tao-surface-brand-1-subtle) 40%, transparent);
    margin-bottom: var(--tao-spacing-lg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .manifesto__avatar-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Left ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .manifesto__left {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--tao-spacing-xl));
  }

  .manifesto__statement {
    font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-lg);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--tao-text-default);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .manifesto__statement strong {
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--tao-text-default);
  }

  /* ── Right ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .manifesto__right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--tao-spacing-xxl);
    padding-top: var(--tao-spacing-xs);
  }

  .manifesto__pillar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr;
    gap: var(--tao-spacing-md);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .manifesto__num {
    font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--tao-text-brand-1);
    opacity: 0.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-top: var(--tao-spacing-xxs);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .manifesto__pillar-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--tao-spacing-sm);
  }

  .manifesto__pillar-title {
    font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--tao-text-default);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .manifesto__pillar-body {
    font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-md);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--tao-text-subtle);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Dividers between pillars ───────────────────────────── */
  .manifesto__pillar + .manifesto__pillar {
    border-top: var(--tao-border-width-sm) solid var(--tao-border-subtle);
    padding-top: var(--tao-spacing-xxl);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .manifesto__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--tao-spacing-xxl);
    }
    .manifesto__left {
      position: static;
    }
    .manifesto__statement {
      font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-xl);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .manifesto__container {
      padding: 0 var(--tao-spacing-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
